1
00:00:16,559 --> 00:00:17,760
You may not know,

2
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:19,199
but since you married into the Shen Family,

3
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:22,600
he never intended for you to have children.

4
00:00:24,079 --> 00:00:25,480
The loss of your child

5
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:26,960
was also his idea.

6
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:29,000
The Su family has always insisted

7
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,760
that the child should take the Su surname.

8
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,479
Rather than wasting this money,

9
00:00:32,679 --> 00:00:35,200
it's better to let me and Shen

10
00:00:35,359 --> 00:00:36,479
enjoy this blessing.

11
00:00:43,880 --> 00:00:44,399
Come on,

12
00:00:53,439 --> 00:00:55,200
save our child.

13
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,200
My dear,

14
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,679
please.

15
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:27,400
Keep yelling,

16
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,560
keep yelling!

17
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,319
No matter how much pain you endure,

18
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,640
you must endure it silently.

19
00:01:41,959 --> 00:01:43,079
You must be virtuous and graceful,

20
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:46,439
never bring shame to the Su Family.

21
00:01:52,319 --> 00:01:53,000
Yi,

22
00:01:53,599 --> 00:01:53,920
you...

23
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,319
Yi,

24
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:00,200
you've always been sensible.

25
00:02:00,799 --> 00:02:02,640
Why are you so confused today?

26
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:06,200
Yes,

27
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,080
I've neglected you lately.

28
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,400
That's just because

29
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,280
the pressure in the court is too great.

30
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:14,199
So I'm not nice to you.

31
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,400
You may forgive me.

32
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,199
I will

33
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:19,439
make it up to you.

34
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,039
I've heard

35
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,599
this too many times.

36
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,759
I know

37
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,319
you're a greedy,

38
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,199
hypocritical,

39
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:34,520
and opportunistic scoundrel.

40
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,039
But...

41
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,120
I actually hoped

42
00:02:39,960 --> 00:02:41,120
that one day,

43
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,560
I could change you.

44
00:02:45,159 --> 00:02:46,039
I was wrong.

45
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:48,120
You'll never change.

46
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,280
You're like

47
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:53,520
a worm in a rotten beam,

48
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,879
eating away the foundation of the Su family

49
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,120
and my life.

50
00:02:59,120 --> 00:02:59,400
You...

51
00:02:59,520 --> 00:02:59,960
Shut up.

52
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,159
You're always like this.

53
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,120
You're just a merchant's daughter,

54
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,520
yet you're so arrogant!

55
00:03:07,639 --> 00:03:09,000
Let go of me!

56
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,240
The Sus have relied on me

57
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,520
for so many advantages.

58
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:15,800
How can you be so ungrateful?

59
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,639
Let go of me!

60
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,439
Let go of me!

61
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:24,479
If you dare to kill yourself again,

62
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,960
I will make sure the Sus

63
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,520
will be ruined forever!

64
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,080
I know I was wrong.

65
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,520
I'll never disobey you again.

66
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,360
Please forgive me.

67
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:58,199
[I'll be in the backyard at midnight.]

68
00:04:46,720 --> 00:04:47,279
My Lord,

69
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,360
how is she doing?

70
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,519
The shop owner

71
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,399
is the wife of Lord Shen,

72
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,560
the West Market Magistrate.

73
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,240
Shen Yuan?

74
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:54,800
Yes.

75
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,759
According to our scouts,

76
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,800
Lady Yin has paid a deposit for a carriage

77
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,920
and is waiting near Shen Residence.

78
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,519
This is absurd!

79
00:05:01,279 --> 00:05:01,879
Sister Su,

80
00:05:02,199 --> 00:05:03,600
find a place to stay for now,

81
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,240
and we'll figure out a way

82
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,199
to transfer your household registration.

83
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,120
Then he won't be able

84
00:05:08,319 --> 00:05:09,399
to make things difficult for you anymore.

85
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,160
Get out of the carriage.

86
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,000
Hurry up.

87
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,639
One.

88
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,680
Two.

89
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,360
Lord Shen.

90
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,879
It's cold at night.

91
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,920
Why make it hard for a weak woman?

92
00:05:38,759 --> 00:05:40,360
Since she's determined to leave,

93
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,959
forcing her

94
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:43,839
will only increase resentment.

95
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,759
Sister Su

96
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:53,279
is determined to leave.

97
00:05:53,639 --> 00:05:55,439
What should be the punishment

98
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,319
for luring and helping a wife escape?

99
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:58,319
My Lord,

100
00:05:58,800 --> 00:05:59,519
according to the law,

101
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:02,160
the punishment is banishment.

102
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,279
I...

103
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,920
I'll go with you.

104
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,000
Lord Zhang,

105
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,279
This way.

106
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:17,399
Isn't this Lord Shen?

107
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,040
What a lively scene.

108
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:23,120
Isn't this the son of Lord Zhang

109
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,000
from the Ministry of Personnel?

110
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,160
You two have arrived just in time.

111
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:30,879
Lord Shen clearly agreed

112
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:33,120
to let me and Sister Su go to Jiangnan.

113
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,279
But for some reason,

114
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,879
he suddenly changed his mind.

115
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,560
I've prepared so many gifts

116
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,199
for the Su family in vain.

117
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,240
Lord Shen,

118
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,040
this is not right of you.

119
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,560
Since you've promised the young lady,

120
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:45,480
how could you break it in public?

121
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,199
If this gets out,

122
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,959
people will say you

123
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,600
have lost your manners.

124
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,480
I just think

125
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,839
it's too hasty at night.

126
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:56,000
I just want to be more prepared,

127
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:58,240
to avoid any inconvenience on the way.

128
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:58,920
Alright.

129
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,639
I know you two

130
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:03,279
are in harmony.

131
00:07:03,839 --> 00:07:05,120
These trivial matters

132
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:08,199
should be left to the women to worry about.

133
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:11,000
A fine night is fleeting.

134
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,240
Why not join me at the Bright Moon Pavilion

135
00:07:13,519 --> 00:07:14,399
for a drink?

136
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,120
Wouldn't that be delightful?

137
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,839
Let's go.

138
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,879
Enough talk.

139
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,519
Let's go.

140
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,360
Still going to drink with courtesans?

141
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:38,480
My lord,

142
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,000
you are being reckless.

143
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,920
Acting without permission,

144
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:49,199
have you thought about the consequences?

145
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,240
If anything goes wrong tonight,

146
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,759
you'll be ruined.

147
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,759
If she accuses you of threatening her,

148
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,120
even the Xiao Family can't protect you.

149
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,800
I'm talking to you!

150
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:03,959
If I had to do it again,

151
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,319
I would do the same.

152
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,000
You...

153
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,639
Thank you for helping me tonight.

154
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,360
Please don't argue over me.

155
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,279
Shen Yuan may be harsh to me,

156
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,279
but he's a court official.

157
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,519
He won't

158
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:23,879
he won't let it out.

159
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:26,920
I'll go back to the Sus tomorrow.

160
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,120
I won't drag you into this.

161
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:30,959
Sister Su,

162
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:32,399
don't say that.

163
00:08:32,879 --> 00:08:33,679
I did this,

164
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:34,960
so I'm not afraid of being implicated.

165
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,360
Sister Su,

166
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:39,519
you'd better not go back to Jiangnan.

167
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,919
You should take care of yourself first.

168
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,200
Otherwise,

169
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,279
your parents

170
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,559
will be worried about you.

171
00:08:47,559 --> 00:08:48,480
Ms Yin,

172
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,360
why are you so nice to me?

173
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,399
At first,

174
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,080
I did pester you every day

175
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,039
to rent this shop.

176
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,799
But when I learned of your situation,

177
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,279
how could I just turn a blind eye?

178
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,639
This world

179
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,559
is already harsh enough on women.

180
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,720
If everyone only cares about themselves,

181
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:10,879
how can women

182
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,799
ever carve out a path for themselves?

183
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:18,879
You're truly noble.

184
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:20,799
You don't have to

185
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:22,279
pay extra rent for this shop.

186
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:25,120
Just consider it an investment from me.

187
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,320
I'm willing to share the

188
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,679
risks and rewards with you.

189
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,639
I will not let you down.

190
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,799
I promise.

191
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,480
But,

192
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,440
I can't show up for now.

193
00:09:39,919 --> 00:09:40,519
I'll have to

194
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:42,639
rely on you to manage the business.

195
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,480
Don't worry.

196
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:47,879
What do you

197
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,679
think of it?

198
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,279
Would you agree

199
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,799
would you have agreed?

200
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:57,600
I didn't know

201
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:59,360
you had such a close relationship

202
00:09:59,519 --> 00:10:00,519
with the Xiao Family.

203
00:10:00,639 --> 00:10:01,159
No, no,

204
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,519
I'm just staying temporarily at his house.

205
00:10:02,519 --> 00:10:03,159
No, no, no,

206
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,000
she is the future

207
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,519
matriarch of the Xiao Family.

208
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,000
The matriarch has worked hard

209
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,399
for the Xiao Family for many years.

210
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,240
The wife of the young master

211
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,519
should have been from the Liu Family.

212
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,799
But now,

213
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,919
the lady of the Yin Family

214
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,480
has been brought home.

215
00:10:26,879 --> 00:10:28,759
A fallen merchant's daughter poses no threat.

216
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:29,879
Besides,

217
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:32,639
Yunzhou believes her father killed his.

218
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,240
It's uncertain how long she'll stay.

219
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:44,399
We'll just wait and see.

220
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:47,759
Yunzhou seems

221
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:49,519
to have more vitality than before.

222
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,679
Now that Madam Yin

223
00:10:53,679 --> 00:10:54,519
is without support,

224
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,879
and you

225
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:58,240
lack a trusted companion,

226
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,720
the Eastern Courtyard has been vacant.

227
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,000
Why not

228
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,919
let my niece move in

229
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,720
to keep you company?

230
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,399
The Eastern Courtyard is too damp

231
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,639
for long-term living.

232
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,000
I won't bother my cousin.

233
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:17,039
Since you're concerned about the Liu family,

234
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,679
why not

235
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,240
go back and help out?

236
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:21,960
You'll be less bored here.

237
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,120
I...

238
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,399
I'm not feeling well.

239
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,440
I'll go back and rest.

240
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:02,519
[Take a look, please.]

241
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,759
[The first women's clinic in Chang'an]

242
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:06,279
[is now open.]

243
00:12:07,799 --> 00:12:08,759
A female healer?

244
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:09,759
How unusual!

245
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,840
She looks barely 20.

246
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:14,240
Who knows if she's any good?

247
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,759
Probably just here to swindle money.

248
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:17,240
In this world,

249
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:18,440
which healer

250
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,600
would teach a woman medicine?

251
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:20,639
It's just

252
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:22,279
the work of midwives and herbalists.

253
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,879
Lady,

254
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,200
if you don't believe me,

255
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,360
I can check your pulse first.

256
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,200
How about that?

257
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,519
I don't want to be

258
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:29,919
a guinea pig.

259
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:30,519
You'll be sorry.

260
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,679
Come and have a look.

261
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,279
The best in Chang'an.

262
00:12:59,639 --> 00:13:01,000
Women practicing medicine?

263
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:03,000
They're just using it as a cover.

264
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:05,600
They're messing up the livelihood of real doctors.

265
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:07,399
If this continues,

266
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:10,000
what will happen to the dignity of medicine?

267
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,440
I've heard what you said.

268
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:14,639
But what do you think

269
00:13:14,799 --> 00:13:15,720
is the true meaning of medicine?
